{"tid":2420084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女子「錢大媽」買菇食物中毒","createTime":"2021-02-23T16:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T07:25:35.000Z","uid":5195,"like":403,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea7dd3687b15e563618d2dfa634892f795675ab","tid":2420084,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"兩名女子分別在家進食菇類後，懷疑食物中毒，昨日到伊利沙伯醫院求醫，情況穩定。衞生防護中心調查發現，涉事菇類，分別購自土瓜灣落山道嶺南大廈地下的「錢大媽」，以及牛池灣街市內一間店舖，中心已通知食物環境衞生署。<br />\n　　 <br />\n兩名女子分別35歲和66歲，昨日在家中烹煮和進食最近購買的菇類，約半小時至一小時後出現噁心、嘔吐和腹痛等徵狀。"},{"pid":"a4617560c00e15069157b4b3d26debe1ab4a2e2b","tid":2420084,"uid":168366,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"$QDM"},{"pid":"df9bdb6add6d8719fc5f1ecc575c9b9073eb8a35","tid":2420084,"uid":17641,"like":318,"dislike":10,"score":308,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>自己身體差瀨錢大媽</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154bfe8b59265d22ba4ceb91bfb6eb32ba057f36","tid":2420084,"uid":79562,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"df9bdb6add6d8719fc5f1ecc575c9b9073eb8a35","tid":2420084,"uid":17641,"like":318,"dislike":10,"score":308,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>自己身體差瀨錢大媽</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09256c58e17e8922086f36fc2e7174ef046fd47","tid":2420084,"uid":11291,"like":154,"dislike":0,"score":154,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNFRhvf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNFRhvf.jpg&h=4ae8a223&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b33dc417d19106766c077284ca696bcc0cc2f5a","tid":2420084,"uid":236